[The Thai health authorities have come up with an aggressive campaign
aimed at bringing under control the dengue fever epidemics across the
country immediately before the rainy season (June - July). The idea
of "Mr. Dengue Fever" is a good model for other dengue-endemic
countries. - Mod.RY]
